All lure spells at level 51 (Damage 640-900) 100% Unresistable<br>
<br>
Harvest II  Level 51  400-850 mana<br>
<br>
Translocate would work out of group.<br>
<br>
Abscond/Evacuate fizzle rate would be zero for the masters of transportation.<br>
<br>
Sunstrike moved to Level 58<br>
<br>
Bane line spells would no longer need regents and would do 4000 dmg for 600 mana.<br>
<br>
Three Level 60 DDs for Cold/Heat/Magic <br>
  Wrath of Graff - Magic 2000 dmg for 500 mana<br>
  Ire of Solusek Ro - Fire 2000 dmg for 500 mana<br>
  Icy Death - Cold 2000 dmg for 500 mana<br>
<br>
An eye spell cast by a planar level Wizard would be able to move to the plane and see what was there.  Duration of existence would increase per level as well as inherent buffs for the eye.<br>
<br>
And finally, bye bye Atols and Bond's for wizzys.  You don't need em anymore.  You have a group!<br>
